  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Vildagliptin in Subjects With Impaired Glucose Tolerance</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Vildagliptin in Subjects With Impaired Glucose Tolerance</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Novartis</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Novartis</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the safety and effectiveness of vildagliptin, an
      unapproved drug, compared to placebo in lowering post-meal blood glucose levels in people
      with pre-diabetes who have high blood sugar levels after meals.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
